notes.h1: SBML model of Cell cycle control mechanism
notes.p: This is a hypothetical model of the cell cycle control mechanism by Chen et al(2004). The model reproduces the time profiles of the different species in Fig 2 of the paper. The figure depicts the cycle of a daughter cell. Since,the Mass Doubling Time(MDT) is 90 minutes, time t=90 from the model simulation will correspond to time t=0 in the paper. The model was successfully tested using MathSBML
